---
// Componente Newsletter - trucos125.com
---
<div class="newsletter-card">
  <div class="content">
    <span class="badge">COMUNIDAD TRUCOS125</span>
    <h3>¡No te pierdas ni un truco!</h3>
    <p>Únete a más de 500 moteros novatos y recibe consejos de mecánica, seguridad y ofertas en equipamiento cada semana.</p>
    
    <form class="newsletter-form">
      <input type="email" placeholder="Tu mejor email..." required />
      <button type="submit">¡QUIERO UNIRME!</button>
    </form>
    <p class="spam-free">🔒 Sin spam. Solo gas del bueno.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .newsletter-card {
    background: #111;
    color: white;
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    margin: 4rem 0;
    text-align: center;
    border-left: 8px solid #e30613;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
  }
  .badge { background: #e30613; padding: 5px 12px; font-weight: 900; font-size: 0.8rem; border-radius: 4px; }
  h3 { font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-size: 2.5rem; margin: 1rem 0; text-transform: uppercase; }
  p { font-size: 1.1rem; color: #ccc; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 2rem; }
  
  .newsletter-form {
    display: flex;
    gap: 10px;
    justify-content: center;
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  
  input {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: none;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }
  
  button {
    background: #e30613;
    color: white;
    border: none;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: transform 0.2s;
  }
  
  button:hover { transform: scale(1.05); background: #be123c; }
  .spam-free { font-size: 0.8rem; margin-top: 1rem; opacity: 0.6; }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .newsletter-form { flex-direction: column; }
    button { padding: 1rem; }
  }
</style>